OL,3,CTheme park to reopen for Easter after
OL,4,Cgoing into liquidation
OL,6,FBrean Theme Park will reopen for the
OL,7,FEaster holidays after an agreement was
OL,8,Freached between the popular Somerset
OL,9,Fattraction and its landlord.
OL,11,FUnity Holidays, who own the site, said
OL,12,Fit would reopen from Friday 3 April
OL,13,F2026 and will remain open throughout
OL,14,Fthe school Easter holidays.
OL,16,FBrean Theme Park, which went into
OL,17,Fliquidation in February and lease the
OL,18,Fsite fron Unity, initially announced
OL,19,Fit would reopen for 2026 on 21 March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
