OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775146264
OL,3,CTheme park to reopen for Easter after
OL,4,Cgoing into liquidation
OL,6,FHowever, visitors reported arriving at
OL,7,Fthe attraction to find it closed.
OL,9,FThe park said on its website that this
OL,10,Fwas due to ongoing issues with
OL,11,Flandlord Unity Holidays, and
OL,12,Fapologised for the inconvenience
OL,13,Fcaused.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Unity Holidays said
OL,16,Fthe temporary closure was due to
OL,17,F"repeated failures by the theme park
OL,18,Foperator to meet key obligations".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
