PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775146264
OL,3,CTheme park to reopen for Easter after
OL,4,Cgoing into liquidation
OL,6,FThey added that work is underway to
OL,7,Fdraw up a new agreement to secure
OL,8,FBrean Theme Park's future.
OL,10,FThis could include new rides, an
OL,11,Fimproved food offering, and an update
OL,12,Fto the park's "overall look and feel".
OL,14,FIt is hoped the new agreement will be
OL,15,Freached by the end of May 2026.
